1
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Episode 12</font>

2
00:02:27,010 --> 00:02:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This day was bound to come eventually.</font>

3
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on!</font>

4
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

5
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember, come back immediately 
once you confirm this is fake.</font>

6
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are all the magical 
artifacts you gave me before.</font>

7
00:02:41,390 --> 00:02:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take them for self-defense.</font>

8
00:02:47,490 --> 00:02:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister!</font>

9
00:02:48,690 --> 00:02:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I shouldn't have doubted you!</font>

10
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know why!</font>

11
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really! I really didn't want to doubt you!</font>

12
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

13
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just remember to come back quickly.</font>

14
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will!</font>

15
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to trouble you three with this.</font>

16
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three days have passed since 
the so-called execution day.</font>

17
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think Ma Xianhong is stupid 
enough to fall for this trap.</font>

18
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we still need to wait?</font>

19
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you guys still waiting?</font>

20
00:03:48,510 --> 00:03:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of the mole?</font>

21
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The intel we're sending back might 
reach the killer and Ma Xianhong.</font>

22
00:03:53,740 --> 00:03:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They might let their guard down.</font>

23
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the plan, right?</font>

24
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heh, and also take a few extra days off.</font>

25
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if he actually shows up?</font>

26
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you be in danger?</font>

27
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang, you were seriously hurt, right?</font>

28
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I brought two masters along.</font>

29
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, if he brings people along,</font>

30
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll escape through the secret 
passage in the bunker.</font>

31
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see... As long as you 
know what you're doing.</font>

32
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

33
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We look forward to good news!</font>

34
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How likely do you think it is
you'll win this bet?</font>

35
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very likely...</font>

36
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The odds of Ma coming here to check on
the Shanggenqi Mutants are very low.</font>

37
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the odds of him coming 
to find me are very high,</font>

38
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because I added
a bit of extra information.</font>

39
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something no one but Ma would notice.</font>

40
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Ma, remember the black 
puppet that got smashed?</font>

41
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Zhang Chulan, did that!</font>

42
00:04:45,570 --> 00:04:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The black puppet
 shouldn't have been there.</font>

43
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adding that changes the 
entire message's meaning.</font>

44
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma, this stupid trap was 
set by me, Zhang Chulan.</font>

45
00:04:58,290 --> 00:05:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to all this trouble just to leave 
a message that only you can understand.</font>

46
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we'll leave after today.</font>

47
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might not come here,</font>

48
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I don't think you'll sit 
still after seeing that message.</font>

49
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you're still alive</font>

50
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and everyone's looking for you,</font>

51
00:05:16,810 --> 00:05:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's best to meet
in this godforsaken place.</font>

52
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, you want to see me, right?</font>

53
00:05:26,140 --> 00:05:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a score to settle with you too!</font>

54
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are...</font>

55
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn! Seeing that face right now 
makes me want to beat the crap out of him!</font>

56
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Control my expression!</font>

57
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Control my expression carefully!</font>

58
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind who I am.</font>

59
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you guys dealt with my friends.</font>

60
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just here to figure out why!</font>

61
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't tell you the specifics,</font>

62
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but suffice to say it's 
a complete fabrication!</font>

63
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In a week at most, you'll be 
able to contact your friends.</font>

64
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't believe me, 
I can take you inside for a look.</font>

65
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It doesn't sound like a lie.</font>

66
00:06:01,740 --> 00:06:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That does put my mind at ease.</font>

67
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you captured them just because 
of a guy called Ma Xianhong?</font>

68
00:06:06,470 --> 00:06:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

69
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is this Ma Xianhong guy?</font>

70
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My friends never mentioned him...</font>

71
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you Ma Xianhong?</font>

72
00:06:14,020 --> 00:06:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone he sent?</font>

73
00:06:19,530 --> 00:06:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

74
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard of that guy.</font>

75
00:06:22,970 --> 00:06:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That... that was close!</font>

76
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought he realized!</font>

77
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No? If not, why only come after 
the execution day has passed?</font>

78
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. If Ma didn't send you,</font>

79
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:34,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then never mind what I'm about to say.</font>

80
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you do know him,</font>

81
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and don't want something 
bad to happen to him,</font>

82
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then pass on this message.</font>

83
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's in grave danger now.</font>

84
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He needs to contact me,</font>

85
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in whatever way he deems safe.</font>

86
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he must contact me.</font>

87
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, let's eat.</font>

88
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

89
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma Xianhong, here's yours...</font>

90
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, no thanks.</font>

91
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bao'er, what did you just call him?</font>

92
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:05,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma Xianhong. Isn't this the guy 
you've been waiting for?</font>

93
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... but his face, height...</font>

94
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, apart from the face and height, 
nothing much has changed.</font>

95
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still the same smell, strong and pungent.</font>

96
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro!</font>

97
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been waiting here for ages!</font>

98
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan! Get up!</font>

99
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you my god-uncle?</font>

100
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't accept this!</font>

101
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was just me running my mouth, Bro!</font>

102
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to forgive your 
mischievous little brother!</font>

103
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bao'er! Didn't I tell you to prepare Bro 
so he can dish out some discipline?</font>

104
00:07:41,110 --> 00:07:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it to him!</font>

105
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

106
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bao'er, do you have a grudge against me?</font>

107
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro, for the sake of our elders,</font>

108
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">please spare my life!</font>

109
00:07:57,850 --> 00:07:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you could remove the 
thorns from the stick,</font>

110
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would be even more grateful!</font>

111
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Heaven Communicating 
Talisman was easier to learn...</font>

112
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turn around!</font>

113
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, Bro!</font>

114
00:08:07,130 --> 00:08:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to turn around and stand up!</font>

115
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan! Don't think I'll let you off
because you're being shameless! Get up!</font>

116
00:08:12,850 --> 00:08:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to go the extra 
mile to correct a mistake!</font>

117
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know how else I can 
convince you I mean you no harm.</font>

118
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a look at this.</font>

119
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:25,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet he won't come!</font>

120
00:08:25,990 --> 00:08:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not betting.</font>

121
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma Xianhong, if you did come,</font>

122
00:08:31,850 --> 00:08:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">well, we're not here anymore.</font>

123
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't do this to catch you.</font>

124
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan just wanted to see you.</font>

125
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're looking to settle scores 
with Zhang Chulan,</font>

126
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">make sure Bao'er records 
a video for us to enjoy.</font>

127
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the kid really 
doesn't owe you anything,</font>

128
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">either in principle or in practice.</font>

129
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you really do lay into him...</font>

130
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, never mind.</font>

131
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget what I said.</font>

132
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not very good at threatening people.</font>

133
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, you went through 
all this trouble just to see me.</font>

134
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly do you want?</font>

135
00:09:07,050 --> 00:09:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To have a heart-to-heart conversation...</font>

136
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro, I'm getting up, I'm getting up!</font>

137
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead. Since you want to talk,</font>

138
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll listen to what you have to say.</font>

139
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our conversation back in the 
village wasn't finished, right?</font>

140
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you my story. 
Now I want to hear yours.</font>

141
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to pump me for information?</font>

142
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want to hear about 
your past with your family,</font>

143
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and about how you lost your memory.</font>

144
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before my grandfather died, he said that</font>

145
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he masterminded the Jiashen rebellion.</font>

146
00:09:34,830 --> 00:09:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in my memory, he never 
complained about his situation.</font>

147
00:09:38,730 --> 00:09:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't see himself as a victim.</font>

148
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He felt he deserved it.</font>

149
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that interesting?</font>

150
00:09:46,070 --> 00:09:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really envy you.</font>

151
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least you got to spend a 
few years with Master Zhang.</font>

152
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never met my great-grandfather,</font>

153
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I often heard my 
grandfather talk about him.</font>

154
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Xianhong! Daydreaming again?</font>

155
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why have you been staring at 
that thing so much lately?</font>

156
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro, haven't you guys noticed...?</font>

157
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to leave Xianhong alone.</font>

158
00:10:14,830 --> 00:10:16,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's always been like that.</font>

159
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who in the village even plays with him?</font>

160
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Xianhong's got a screw 
loose from being alone too much.</font>

161
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two little rascals!
 What are you saying?</font>

162
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather!</font>

163
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, what's wrong with Xianhong?</font>

164
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Grandfather, didn't you make 
a bead for everyone in the family?</font>

165
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong said if you stare at that 
thing long enough, it'll glow!</font>

166
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What do you mean, Father?</font>

167
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want Xianhong to learn from you?</font>

168
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, did you make all of these?</font>

169
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, do you want to learn 
how to make these with me?</font>

170
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

171
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your great-grandfather taught 
me how to make these.</font>

172
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, he said,</font>

173
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Yuanlu, you know...</font>

174
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not qualified to pass this on to you.</font>

175
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not worthy!"</font>

176
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He also said,</font>

177
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Yuanlu, I understand
all these principles,</font>

178
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I still can't get 
past this mental barrier.</font>

179
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These skills were created by my own hands,</font>

180
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I really don't want them 
to die out there.</font>

181
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, I was too young to understand 
what your great-grandfather meant.</font>

182
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't until I fully inherited 
his techniques that I realized.</font>

183
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I can't bear to let them be lost either!"</font>

184
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just a kid back then.</font>

185
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I have understood 
what he was talking about?</font>

186
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From then on, I lived with 
Grandpa and learned from him.</font>

187
00:11:57,210 --> 00:12:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking back, I think he was 
testing me in every way,</font>

188
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he was also hesitant.</font>

189
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only you weren't cut out for it,</font>

190
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or if Master Yuanlu had been 
ruthless and let it die out,</font>

191
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we wouldn't have so many problems today.</font>

192
00:12:13,710 --> 00:12:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, I think you're heartless.</font>

193
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

194
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on! Continue, continue!</font>

195
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather! Look at mine!</font>

196
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's this? Check out this work!</font>

197
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not finished yet!</font>

198
00:12:28,140 --> 00:12:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've only been learning from 
my father for a few days.</font>

199
00:12:33,310 --> 00:12:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

200
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Better than Xianhong, right?</font>

201
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you teach me too?</font>

202
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, get out of here!</font>

203
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your old man's skills are more 
than enough to teach you!</font>

204
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong, everyone else
has already finished.</font>

205
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you still fiddling 
with this one part?</font>

206
00:13:02,650 --> 00:13:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, maybe I'm really 
just not cut out for this?</font>

207
00:13:06,650 --> 00:13:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't trying to compete with Xianhe.</font>

208
00:13:09,210 --> 00:13:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now that I've started, 
I can't let this material down...</font>

209
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let this material down?</font>

210
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Once this material is in my hands,</font>

211
00:13:19,770 --> 00:13:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what it ultimately becomes 
is entirely up to me.</font>

212
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen good things.</font>

213
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your products are all
good things. They glow.</font>

214
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything that passes through my hands,</font>

215
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even the tiniest component,</font>

216
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if I don't see that light, I won't let go.</font>

217
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong,</font>

218
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all these years, I've been watching you.</font>

219
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, I will pass on to you the true
skills your great-grandfather taught me.</font>

220
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you must swear to me!</font>

221
00:13:51,810 --> 00:13:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never show anyone the artifacts 
created using the methods I teach you!</font>

222
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may only use them when you 
and our family are in danger!</font>

223
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And after that?</font>

224
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't follow Master Yuanlu's words, 
and revealed Divine Craftsmanship.</font>

225
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't.</font>

226
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until those people came for us,</font>

227
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always kept my promise to Grandfather.</font>

228
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, what happened?</font>

229
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone chopped off his leg!</font>

230
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

231
00:14:19,310 --> 00:14:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, what's the matter?</font>

232
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

233
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

234
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong, go get my...</font>

235
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my tools and yours, and bring them here.</font>

236
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then come see me.</font>

237
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rest of you, get out!</font>

238
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you, out!</font>

239
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:41,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, I've brought 
everything you asked for.</font>

240
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who on earth did this to you?</font>

241
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know them!</font>

242
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong, take the family and leave!</font>

243
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Escape now! Don't worry about me.</font>

244
00:14:53,270 --> 00:14:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I...</font>

245
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never abandon you, Grandfather!</font>

246
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather!</font>

247
00:14:59,130 --> 00:15:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go! They're coming...</font>

248
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're coming to
steal Divine Craftsmanship.</font>

249
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your great-grandfather Benzai 
passed away so many years ago.</font>

250
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was careless! They never gave up!</font>

251
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong, you must understand 
how dangerous this is for us!</font>

252
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They haven't made their next move yet.</font>

253
00:15:20,090 --> 00:15:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're giving me a chance!</font>

254
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They want me to hand over 
Divine Craftsmanship!</font>

255
00:15:26,230 --> 00:15:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

256
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run, all of you! Run as far as you can!</font>

257
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just a burden to you now!</font>

258
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! Either we leave together,</font>

259
00:15:34,850 --> 00:15:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or I'll stay behind and
fight them with you!</font>

260
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not leaving you alone here.</font>

261
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So stubborn!</font>

262
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a good kid in every way,</font>

263
00:15:49,010 --> 00:15:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but so stubborn!</font>

264
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:54,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine then, let's go see the others first.</font>

265
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, sir, why are you getting up?</font>

266
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be discharged yet!</font>

267
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here.</font>

268
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather, slow down!</font>

269
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me help you!</font>

270
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need!</font>

271
00:16:21,810 --> 00:16:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I need help just to walk,</font>

272
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then I'm really a burden to you!</font>

273
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened after?</font>

274
00:16:41,470 --> 00:16:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Master Yuanlu went home.</font>

275
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened next?</font>

276
00:16:45,380 --> 00:16:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already told you what I can tell you.</font>

277
00:16:48,450 --> 00:16:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that means...</font>

278
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you lost the memories of 
your family from then on.</font>

279
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't tell me
what happened after that.</font>

280
00:16:55,650 --> 00:16:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The memories after that</font>

281
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">must be related to the people 
we're up against, right?</font>

282
00:16:59,930 --> 00:17:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly are you trying to say?</font>

283
00:17:02,470 --> 00:17:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to confirm something first,</font>

284
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in case you were involved.</font>

285
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you do this?</font>

286
00:17:07,890 --> 00:17:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

287
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Guo Liang?</font>

288
00:17:12,570 --> 00:17:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever suspected 
the people around you?</font>

289
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

290
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, you're here to sow discord.</font>

291
00:17:21,390 --> 00:17:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's wrong with Ma 
Xianhong's current condition.</font>

292
00:17:24,850 --> 00:17:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any normal person would 
definitely be suspicious</font>

293
00:17:28,110 --> 00:17:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if they went through what he did.</font>

294
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless I can figure out what the 
people behind Ma did to him,</font>

295
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be able to get him 
to come over to our side.</font>

296
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down! I'm just here to pass on a
message from our Company's Chairman Zhao.</font>

297
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chairman Zhao? Zhao Fangxu?</font>

298
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan. I mobilized 
the Company's resources</font>

299
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and went to all this trouble to help 
you carry out this entrapment plan.</font>

300
00:17:50,810 --> 00:17:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you want me to let him go?</font>

301
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And call off
the Company's manhunt for him?</font>

302
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How does the Company benefit from that?</font>

303
00:17:57,470 --> 00:17:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Ma Xianhong really shows up,</font>

304
00:17:59,970 --> 00:18:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it proves there's a rift between 
him and the people behind him.</font>

305
00:18:03,010 --> 00:18:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's already a gain from this operation.</font>

306
00:18:04,810 --> 00:18:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To deal with someone like Ma Xianhong,</font>

307
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need to show goodwill.</font>

308
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to win him over!</font>

309
00:18:10,850 --> 00:18:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand what you mean.</font>

310
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why would I go to all this trouble?</font>

311
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard that Chou Rang still 
hasn't backed down, right?</font>

312
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think you can handle his idol 
Ma Xianhong with forceful methods?</font>

313
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've given this some consideration.</font>

314
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if we can get the 
Lyu family to cooperate,</font>

315
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and use their Bright Soul Skill?</font>

316
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Zhang?</font>

317
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you laughing?</font>

318
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing, I didn't realize you'd 
already given this so much thought.</font>

319
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you being sarcastic?</font>

320
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not!</font>

321
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a big shot with 
unparalleled foresight!</font>

322
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You handle things far more 
thoroughly than us small fry!</font>

323
00:18:49,830 --> 00:18:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut the crap. Tell me!</font>

324
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you really think?</font>

325
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a good idea.</font>

326
00:18:57,730 --> 00:19:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bright Soul Skill might even 
help Ma recover his memories.</font>

327
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if we just grab him 
and mess with his head,</font>

328
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then after that, we'd have 
to lock him up forever,</font>

329
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or kill him.</font>

330
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given Ma's character,</font>

331
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he'd definitely become the 
Company's mortal enemy.</font>

332
00:19:13,410 --> 00:19:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what? What's that got to do with you?</font>

333
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I'm saying!</font>

334
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What influence could a 
little ant like me have?</font>

335
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll follow your orders.</font>

336
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chairman Zhao?</font>

337
00:19:27,810 --> 00:19:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always wondered,</font>

338
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what did Master Xu see in you?</font>

339
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you teasing me?</font>

340
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not teasing you.</font>

341
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid of you, big shot!</font>

342
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big shots have foresight,</font>

343
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they often don't notice 
the little ants at their feet.</font>

344
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:49,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's usually the little ants 
that can bite the big shots!</font>

345
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I really handled 
Ma Xianhong so brutally,</font>

346
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would you be disappointed in me?</font>

347
00:19:58,210 --> 00:19:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be surprised.</font>

348
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think someone like that</font>

349
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would've joined Master 
Xu in protecting Bao'er.</font>

350
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, I'll consider what you said.</font>

351
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are two conditions.</font>

352
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, you need to confirm that you 
didn't kill any Company personnel.</font>

353
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Second, the conflict between you and the 
Company isn't completely resolved yet.</font>

354
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After we deal with the current situation,</font>

355
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can sit down and discuss 
the matters regarding</font>

356
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Divine Craftsmanship and 
the Cultivation Furnace.</font>

357
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the meantime, you can go anywhere,</font>

358
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the Company won't 
consider you a fugitive.</font>

359
00:20:32,950 --> 00:20:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. I heard you're 
looking for your family?</font>

360
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it comes to finding people,</font>

361
00:20:39,330 --> 00:20:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Company is definitely more capable 
than you and your companions.</font>

362
00:20:42,850 --> 00:20:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

363
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, you're still 
trying to sow discord,</font>

364
00:20:46,870 --> 00:20:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to pick us off one by one, right?</font>

365
00:20:50,770 --> 00:20:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're thinking the worst of us.</font>

366
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Ma, you're not so powerful that</font>

367
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Company can't handle things 
without getting rid of you.</font>

368
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I genuinely don't want you to go 
down with the people behind you.</font>

369
00:21:01,910 --> 00:21:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're actually a decent person.</font>

370
00:21:04,300 --> 00:21:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I ever done anything bad?</font>

371
00:21:07,410 --> 00:21:10,100
