373
00:21:12,470 --> 00:21:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Company is definitely more capable 
than you and your companions.</font>

374
00:21:15,970 --> 00:21:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about it carefully...</font>

375
00:21:21,850 --> 00:21:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma!</font>

376
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really screwed me 
over back in the village.</font>

377
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan,</font>

378
00:21:28,090 --> 00:21:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't trust a word you say anymore.</font>

379
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

380
00:21:35,250 --> 00:21:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, Ma!</font>

381
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've only met a few times in total.</font>

382
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have no reason to trust me!</font>

383
00:21:41,100 --> 00:21:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your lost memories and 
missing family might be</font>

384
00:21:43,850 --> 00:21:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">connected to the people around you now!</font>

385
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't believe that either!</font>

386
00:21:47,770 --> 00:21:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, are you saying Sister—</font>

387
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind, Ma!</font>

388
00:21:54,470 --> 00:21:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the point.</font>

389
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The point is, I can't be 
trusted, and not just me!</font>

390
00:21:58,220 --> 00:21:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't trust anyone!</font>

391
