<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't trust anyone...</font>

394
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't trust anyone...</font>

395
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't trust anyone?</font>

396
00:22:18,430 --> 00:22:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't trust anyone?</font>

397
00:22:20,020 --> 00:22:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma, you...</font>

398
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan!</font>

399
00:22:28,210 --> 00:22:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan!</font>

400
00:22:28,210 --> 00:22:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine!</font>

401
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't move!</font>

402
00:22:49,970 --> 00:22:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Catch.</font>

403
00:22:53,670 --> 00:22:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is... a magical artifact?</font>

404
00:22:55,820 --> 00:22:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it for? How do I use it?</font>

405
00:22:58,300 --> 00:22:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma!</font>

406
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't follow me!</font>

407
00:23:00,410 --> 00:23:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me think alone for a while.</font>

408
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least leave a phone number, Ma!</font>

409
00:23:10,630 --> 00:23:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Zhang Chulan?</font>

410
00:23:12,690 --> 00:23:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking?</font>

411
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you said, Ma Xianhong 
really did show up,</font>

412
00:23:17,670 --> 00:23:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he didn't turn on you.</font>

413
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you achieved your objectives?</font>

414
00:23:25,710 --> 00:23:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, something's wrong.</font>

415
00:23:34,270 --> 00:23:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Lingyu, Bao'er, 
a slight change of plans.</font>

416
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go after him! Go after Ma Xianhong!</font>

